parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intermittent No-Start Condition due to Passlock Sensor Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Passlock sensor can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, which can be a safety concern, especially in remote areas or during emergency situations.
symptoms: the Passlock security light will flash
and the vehicle will not crank until the light goes off

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle will stall or lose power
the instrument panel lights will dim
and the ABS and brake warning indicators will illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to not start, which can be a safety concern, especially in remote areas or during emergency situations.
symptoms: the ignition switch will need to be replaced
and the Passlock security light will flash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake light switch can cause the brake lights to malfunction, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake lights will not function properly
and the brake warning indicator will illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system control module can cause intermittent loss of power, stalling, and rapid acceleration, leading to hazardous driving conditions and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Intermittent loss of power when pressing the gas pedal
and water in the fuel module.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion of the fuel pump line can cause major fuel leakage, leading to an extreme fire hazard and toxic gas fumes inside the vehicle.
symptoms: and toxic gas fumes inside the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality to occupants.

wires fractured in the airbag wire harness
